PROJECT 1: Secure VPC Architecture

What I built:
- Custom VPC with CIDR 10.0.0.0/16
- Public subnet (internet facing)
- Private subnet (secure, no internet)
- Internet Gateway attached
- Route Table with internet route
- Security Group (HTTP, HTTPS, SSH rules)
- Network ACL (extra security layer)
- VPC Flow Logs → CloudWatch

Security concepts applied:
- Network segmentation (public vs private)
- Least privilege network access
- Defence in depth (SG + NACL together)
- Full network traffic logging
